{"tid":906493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"顯徑邨10歲仔企圖吊頸 舅父發現救回","createTime":"2018-11-18T04:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T05:46:24.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd5963c5c256f610ce5eb019ec658f1608a317b","tid":906493,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"大圍顯徑邨顯揚樓，昨晚11時許，一名姓冼(10歲)男童致電繼父，聲稱往上址舊居後樓梯上吊，繼父通知男童的舅父，其後在5樓梯間將他尋獲。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，撿獲遺書及一條約1.5米長已打結的繩。男童沒有受傷，其後送院檢查。據稱，男童與母及繼父同住禾輋邨，懷疑受生活問題困擾，警方調查沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=LeNpBdcj6I5QCBKhB5VE%2BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f7a63c43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181118/58926937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58926937&d=LeNpBdcj6I5QCBKhB5VE%2BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9d7b3ac1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58926937&h=4dd74387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181118/58926937</a>"},{"pid":"de985e8ee921cf27c61fc9bebadb7e2a0b977e87","tid":906493,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"阻人刷首抽"},{"pid":"79d056ac5184f3bb2d03950c77879862b083777c","tid":906493,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"有咩咁困擾？"},{"pid":"fa00924c64e713980e0a434df8a48d00d3bcec23","tid":906493,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":8,"s